(18513, 'Erec 100mg 12 f.c. tablets', 'اريك 100مجم 12 قرص', '100.5', '144', 'Sildenafil', 'Adwia', 'Tablet', 'أقراص', 'مقوي للرجال', 'Tonic for men', '100mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
